{"tid":1998984,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Jennie 開箱 GENTLE MONSTER 系列","createTime":"2020-05-02T22:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T18:37:59.000Z","uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e02c0169f2750039263d82603466275f3ef62479","tid":1998984,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T22:04:09.000Z","msg":"雖然還沒回歸，不過成員們也沒忘了要跟粉絲們互動，叻莉莎前陣子拍了辣舞影片、智秀跟玫瑰也上傳了近況跟粉絲們分享；成員Jennie則是拍攝了時尚雜誌，並跟潮流墨鏡品牌GENTLE MONSTER合作了一系列由她親自設計的墨鏡。此次與GENTLE MONSTER聯名系列取名為「Jentle House」，以Jennie回憶中的娃娃屋作為靈感創作，Jentle則是Jennie的「J」以及GENTLE MONSTER的「GENTLE」合在一起，表示合作的概念。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/02/99/7818338.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F02%2F99%2F7818338.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=62617e80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8b65fdec9a4f8e8c321f6e79341d656b99678c0","tid":1998984,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T22:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/02/99/7818340.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F02%2F99%2F7818340.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=e7ceb008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/23/004058_8fc20a7669aa3f4f43c89b7311e5dfde.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F23%2F004058_8fc20a7669aa3f4f43c89b7311e5dfde.gif&h=a432cf09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ba8d0663b2d71af0897e6d043fe1f771a83b9a9","tid":1998984,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T22:04:33.000Z","msg":"Jennie設計的墨鏡一共有四款，分別是以愛犬Kuma為名的「Kuku」、她本人出生的年份「1996」、最喜歡的花朵「Daisy」，以及又潮又文青的「IN THE MOOD」。Jennie將她喜歡的元素通通融合進了墨鏡中，除了有她本身就很愛的貓眼設計，還有豹紋、粉嫩色系、膠框等等亮點，整個系列作品超有她的風格跟態度。"},{"pid":"31d500ccd5ff8e629d8ec9d31db992b96d890a8d","tid":1998984,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T22:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/02/99/7818337.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F02%2F99%2F7818337.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=c358793a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b2802e49f87ea708a0492e7db58472989303801","tid":1998984,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T22:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/02/99/7818339.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F02%2F99%2F7818339.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=efe98362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/23/004058_8fc20a7669aa3f4f43c89b7311e5dfde.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F23%2F004058_8fc20a7669aa3f4f43c89b7311e5dfde.gif&h=a432cf09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89e4f7947f0a82d3b8b45362f79d6e53ef19ab72","tid":1998984,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T22:05:11.000Z","msg":"GENTLE MONSTER也為此打造了專門放置「Jentle House」的娃娃屋，不僅配色、擺飾超級美，重點是還可以開燈！整個少女心十足！讓人不禁聯想Jennie記憶中的娃娃屋實體是什麼夢幻模樣。而Jennie身為設計師，在墨鏡亮相後也積極宣傳，不僅與新銳攝影師Hugo Comte合作拍了一系列時尚大片，還親自開箱直播給粉絲們看，重點是她昨天一連換上了九套衣服，搭配每副墨鏡，完美演繹出「Jentle House」的特有風格。"},{"pid":"22736304261126abaff3387f26ec506b16b20ef4","tid":1998984,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T22:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/02/99/7818341.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F02%2F99%2F7818341.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=6a464dea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/23/004058_8fc20a7669aa3f4f43c89b7311e5dfde.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F23%2F004058_8fc20a7669aa3f4f43c89b7311e5dfde.gif&h=a432cf09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48e0e0c77add6f31fc24a91e22aa5340d95a959d","tid":1998984,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T22:05:34.000Z","msg":"除了服裝外，她也換了各種不同的妝容還有四種髮型，全部的穿搭照都是在床上完成，讓人不禁聯想到超模貝拉哈蒂德近日也開始「居家辦公」，待在家照樣能拍出時尚大片。另外，「Jentle House」除了墨鏡之外，還有三組超潮的小配件，那就是近年來很流行的眼鏡鍊，上面還鑲有Jentle字樣，非常有個性。這三組分別是代表銀色的MOONLIGHT、金色的SUNLIGHT，以及ONYX黑色瑪瑙，就連裝這些配件的包裝盒也超有質感。"},{"pid":"1b2366628dc539d0055a16dea10de76d7b97c724","tid":1998984,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T22:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/02/99/7818355.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F02%2F99%2F7818355.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=7f7fbb08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/23/004058_8fc20a7669aa3f4f43c89b7311e5dfde.gif\" da